                    <span>Dr Stanley goes over and above the call of duty with this great work. Networking With The Affluent will show you how to penetrate the affluent market...network with it's members and key players within their group.<p>This book will create relationships that many have heretofore, been unable to penetrate.<p>Great book by Dr. Stanley.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A very under-rated book! Where are the readers?</div>
